{{!< default}}
{{! The tag above means - insert everything in this file into the {body} of the default.hbs template }}

<div class="container-fluid content fadeIn animated">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-lg-12">
			<h1 class="hidden">{{@blog.title}}</h1>

			<div class="title-container">
				<h1 class="fadeInDown animated title"></h1>
			</div><!-- /.title -->

			<hr>

			<div class="col-lg-6 padding-right left-column">
				<p>Actually I'm just Aaron's website, where he posts some things that are on his mind. They are likely of very little relevance to you or anyone else. With that said, you can scroll down to check them out.</p>
			</div><!-- /.col -->

			<div class="col-lg-6 padding-left right-column">
				<p>If you'd like some background on Aaron see his <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-Lzv1r2d0hVYIjVsJ3oDuBMbwm5SmRU-jRIWJsa5O0g/pub" target="_blank" class="button blue-yellow">resume</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kaarontaylor" target="_blank" class="button linkedin">LinkedIn</a> profile or his very underwhelming <a href="https://github.com/yourfriendaaron" target="_blank" class="button dark">GitHub</a>.</p>
			</div><!-- /.col -->

			<div class="col-lg-12 full-column">
				<p><br>If you'd like to chat send an electronic carrier pigeon to <span class="button underline">mail@aaron.tl</span></p>
			</div><!-- /.col -->

			<div class="col-lg-12">
				<h2>Posts</h2>
				<hr class="tiny">
			</div><!-- /.col -->
		</div><!-- /.col -->
	</div><!-- /.row -->
</div><!-- /.featured-top -->

{{! The main content area on the homepage }}
<main id="content" class="work" role="main">
	<div class="col-sm-12 no-padding">
		{{! The tag below includes the post loop - partials/loop.hbs }}
		{{> "loop"}}
	</div><!-- /.col -->
</main>

<script>
	$(function(){
		$(".title").typed({
			strings: ["Hi, I'm Aaron."],
			typeSpeed: 60,
			showCursor: true,
			startDelay: 600
		});
	});
</script>